DATE:30/01/18

URL:http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/several-soldiers-injured-as-militants-open-fire-at-army-convoy/article18712452.ece

TITLE:One killed, 5 injured as militants open fire on Army convoy 

CONTENT:One soldier was killed and five others were injured when militants opened fire on an Army convoy on the Srinagar-Jammu highway on Saturday morning.

Preliminary reports suggest that the attack place at Hillar, Qazigund, in South Kashmir. The area is over 70 km south of Srinagar.

A police official said a search operation was launched in the area to nab the attackers.

Reinforcements have been rushed to the spot.
